&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Emacs</category><category>GTD</category><category>Org-mode</category><guid>https://lengyueyang.github.io/posts/use-org-mode-to-gtdzh_cn/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 28 Feb 2016 11:26:52 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Spacemacs 学习</title><link>https://lengyueyang.github.io/posts/spacemacs-learningzh_cn/</link><dc:creator>冷月阳</dc:creator><description>&lt;div id="outline-container-sec-1" class="outline-2"&gt;
&lt;h2 id="sec-1"&gt;Useful keybinding&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1"&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id="outline-container-sec-1-1" class="outline-3"&gt;
&lt;h3 id="sec-1-1"&gt;Memory&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-1"&gt;
&lt;ul class="org-ul"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SPC f s Save a buffer
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SPC f S Save all opened buffers
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SPC b b Open or switch a buffer with helm
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SPC T h Select a theme using a helm buffer
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SPC f/p t To toggle the Neotree buffer press (project)
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SPC h b Open the bookmark
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SPC h l Resume the last helm buffers
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SPC s L Focus the last converted search buffer
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;F3 In a helm buffer, convert a helm search buffer into a regular buffer
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

